Joni Mitchell has suffered from Morgellons disease for most of her life . 
  She has been hospitalized after being found unconscious at her home . 
  Sufferers say they are constantly itching and have large sores on their skin from which colorful fibers grow . 
  The medical community believes the disease is likely a mental illness and that sufferers are anxious, depressed or even suffering from substance abuse . 
  Joni Mitchell has been fighting to have the disease recognized as a medical condition . 
 